    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit delivers linear power through a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity during high-G cornering. The suspension retains its sharp damping characteristics, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the tactile feedback synonymous with this chassis. While displaying honest aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain is robust, making this an ideal specimen for the driver who prioritizes peak mechanical performance and analog engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
