    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect blend of sophisticated style and dependable performance. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, expected character marks of a carefully driven vehicle. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the smoke-free leather upholstery is supple and clean, complemented by a fully functional suite of electronics including a premium audio system and dual-zone climate control. Under the hood, the car is mechanically robust, benefiting from a recent comprehensive service and a fresh set of all-season tires. It shifts seamlessly and handles the road with a quiet, confident composure. This is a complete package for a discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine care since day one.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
