      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, which stands as a testament to rigorous care and consistent mechanical upkeep. This unit has been subjected to a comprehensive professional inspection, ensuring that all systems operate with precision and reliability. The exterior retains its original luster, while the interior remains refined and free of significant wear. For the executive or enthusiast seeking a dependable, high-performance vehicle without the premium of a showroom-new price point, this offering represents an outstanding acquisition.",
